feat2 <- read.csv('featuring_2019.csv')
head(feat2)
#   
feat2 %>% 
  as_tbl_graph(directed=FALSE) %>% 
  ggraph(layout = 'nicely') + 
    geom_edge_link() +
    geom_node_point() +
    geom_node_text(aes(label=name))

# ,   
feat2 %>% 
  as_tbl_graph(directed=FALSE) %>%
  mutate(degree = centrality_degree(),   #   ,   
         group = group_infomap())    #

feat2 %>%
  as_tbl_graph(directed=FALSE) %>%
  mutate(degree = centrality_degree(),
         group = group_infomap()) %>%
  ggraph(layout = 'nicely') +
    geom_edge_link() +
    geom_node_point(aes(color=factor(group),   size=degree)) +    #   ,  
    geom_node_text(aes(label=name))    #  

feat2 %>%
  as_tbl_graph(directed=FALSE) %>%
  activate(nodes) %>%
  mutate(degree = centrality_degree(),
         group = group_infomap()) %>%
  ggraph(layout = 'nicely') +
    geom_edge_link(color='gray50') +    #   
    geom_node_point(aes(color=factor(group), size=degree)) +
    geom_node_text(aes(label=name), size=3)   #   

#   ,   
feat2 %>%
  as_tbl_graph(directed=FALSE) %>% 
  activate(nodes) %>%
  mutate(eigen = centrality_eigen(),   #()  
    group = group_infomap()) %>%
  ggraph(layout = 'nicely') +
    geom_edge_link(color='gray50', alpha=.2) +   #  20% 
    geom_node_point(aes(color=factor(group), size=eigen)) +
    geom_node_text(aes(label=name), size=3, repel=TRUE)   #   repel=TRUE 

#,  
feat2 %>%
  as_tbl_graph(directed=FALSE) %>%
  activate(nodes) %>%
  mutate(eigen = centrality_eigen(),
         group = group_infomap()) %>%
  ggraph(layout='nicely') +
    geom_edge_link(color='gray50', alpha=.2, arrow=NULL) +
    geom_node_point(aes(color=factor(group), size=eigen)) +
    geom_node_text(aes(label=name), size=3, repel=TRUE) +
    theme_graph() +   # 
    theme(legend.position='none')    #
